I ended the piece about the project with a beckoning: =E2=80=9CPublishers=
=2C nota bene =E2=80=94 this is the kind of project begging to be a beauti=
ful book.=E2=80=9D

Princeton Architectural Press took note and Dear Data (http://www.amazon.c=
