s now a book=2C for which I had the pleasure of writing the foreword. Expe=
riencing the project anew=2C in this beautiful analog form=2C only amplifi=
es its deeply humane ethos of reclaiming the living texture of =E2=80=9Cda=
ta=E2=80=9D in our everyday lives from the word=E2=80=99s unfeeling=2C alg=
orithmic=2C non-human connotations.

