 Even in Paris=2C I could not shake the old ways=2C the instinct to watch=
 my back at every pass=2C and always be ready to go. </p><p style=3D"-webk=
it-text-size-adjust: 100%;-ms-text-size-adjust: 100%;color: #808080;font-f=
