t my new friend simply showed me the building=2C shook my hand=2C gave a f=
ine <em>bonne soir=C3=A9e</em>=2C and walked off into the wide open night.=
 And watching him walk away=2C I felt that I had missed part of the experi=
ence because of my eyes=2C because my eyes were made in Baltimore=2C becau=
se my eyes were blindfolded by fear. What I wanted was to put as much dist=
